  COLPROCE journals.
\item
  Winner of fifth place among 174 investigations of the Call For Papers
  SIECA 2020 regional contest (Analysis of the use of trade agreements)
\item
  I have been invited to give numerous presentations and webinars on
  economics, commerce and the economic situation at universities,
  government institutions and companies.
\item
  I have knowledge of scientific research protocol, statistics,
  mathematics, econometrics, programming and BigData
\item
  Passionate about science, self-taught.
\end{itemize}

